Packages
it.unical.inf.wsportal.client This package contains a single class that is the entry point of the web application.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.client.callback Contains classes that act as callbacks for asynchronous calls between the client (GUI) and the server components (JSP/Servlet), and for the GUI events.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.client.controller This package contains the class Controller that handles events triggered by the GUI.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.client.model Contains classes that describe the client-side application state.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.client.util Contains utility classes that provide different services on the client side.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.client.view Contains classes that implement the view of the application.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.server This package contains classes that define the server-side components.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.server.db Contains classes that manage the connection to the database and provide the necessary methods to perform SQL queries/manipulation.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.server.servlet Contains classes that serve as Servlets for the web application.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.server.util Contains utility classes that provide different services on the server side.
it.unical.inf.wsportal.shared Contains classes that can be used both on client and server side.
